</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the cover towards you and remove the cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-512698AA-71C0-416F-85FD-2ABD33760541" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F5678BD3-CA91-4530-B428-A07E12DC9D45-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F5678BD3-CA91-4530-B428-A07E12DC9D45-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Move the 5 locking handles to the lower position. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Unlock the mechanism manually (small screwdriver). 
</p><note type="caution" id="GUID-85DB55FD-D23F-4B17-BC33-4B81B2CCF6B0" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The knife of the ink refill units is behind the cover. 
